<P>
 Hooligan alert: A resident wrote to the Pasadena Weekly, acknowledging that 
World Cup officials in Pasadena should be wary of the possibility of the 
"mindless ferocity" of visiting fans. 
</P>
<P>
 English hooligans? No. German hooligans? No. South American hooligans? No. 
</P>
<P>
 He was referring to Raiders hooligans. miscelLAny: 
</P>
