<TEXT>
<P>
 Apple Unveils New PowerBooks: Apple Computer introduced new PowerBook notebook 
computers featuring an innovative way to move the cursor.Instead of a trackball 
or mouse, the four new PowerBook 500 models feature a touch-sensitive 
rectangular area below the space bar. The cursor is moved by running a finger 
over the space. The new machines and two sub-notebook versions are immediately 
available and replace most existing PowerBooks. Apple also cut prices of its 
older PowerBooks and several other computers by up to 27%. 
