<DATE>
<P>
May 17, 1994, Tuesday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
807 words 
</P>
