<P>
 American Health Services Corp.: The Newport Beach operator of diagnostic 
imaging centers lost $344,115, or 4 cents a share, for the first quarter. That 
compared to a loss of $614,735, or 6 cents a share, for the same period in 
1993. Revenue dropped 5% to $9.2 million from $9.7 million. 
</P>
