<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL EARNINGS: MARTIN LAWRENCE REDUCES LOSS TO $599,000 IN QUARTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Martin Lawrence Limited Editions Inc., the Van Nuys marketer of limited 
edition artworks, said it narrowed its loss in the first quarter to $599,000 
from $1.77 million the previous year. The loss was on revenue of $4.68 million, 
down from $4.74 million in 1993. 
</P>
<P>
 The company attributed its improved performance to reduction of overhead costs 
in producing goods and to higher retail prices. 
</P>
