<DOCNO> LA051794-0310 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 042689 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 17, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
