</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Swimming -- In a story on the Southern Section Division II championships in 
Sunday's Times Orange County, it should have read that Los Alamitos' Tim Haney 
won the 500 freestyle in 4 minutes 29.34 seconds. Irvine's Wendy O'Brien's 
winning time in the 50 freestyle championship race was 23.57. 
</P>
</TEXT>
